title: Sword Art Online - Material Edition Soushuuhen (Doujinshi)
description:
Self-published books by Kawahara Reki on [url=https://mangadex.com/manga/1360]Sword Art Online[/url], under the pen-name of Kunori Fumio. Mainly contains side stories to complement the series.

Note: Part comic/novel doujinshi.
